## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="575da-103"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase>類別是抽象的基底類別，用來按鈕欄位，並包含方法和屬性通用於所有按鈕欄位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-103">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase> class is the abstract base class for button fields and contains the methods and properties that are common to all button fields.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="575da-104">這個類別是抽象的因為您無法直接建立它的執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-104">Because this class is abstract, you cannot create an instance of it directly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="575da-105">相反地，您必須建立繼承自非抽象類別的執行個體<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase>類別，例如<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonField>或<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CommandField>類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-105">Instead, you must create an instance of a non-abstract class that inherits from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase> class, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonField> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CommandField> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="575da-106">衍生自物件<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase>用資料繫結控制項 (例如<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>和<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>控制項) 以顯示一或多個按鈕會顯示每一筆記錄。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-106">An object that is derived from the  <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase> is used by data-bound controls (such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> controls) to display one or more buttons for each record that is displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="575da-107">按鈕欄位是根據使用它的資料繫結控制項的顯示方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-107">A button field is displayed differently depending on the data-bound control in which it is used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="575da-108">例如，<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>控制會顯示按鈕欄位做為資料行，但<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>控制項顯示為一個資料列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-108">For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control displays a button field as a column, whereas the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control displays it as a row.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="575da-109">按一下按鈕欄位中的按鈕，就會引發命令事件的父資料繫結控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-109">Clicking a button in a button field raises the command event of the parent data-bound control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="575da-110">您可以提供要藉由提供命令事件的事件處理常式在按一下按鈕時執行的自訂常式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-110">You can provide a custom routine to perform when a button is clicked by providing an event handler for the command event.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="575da-111"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>控制引發<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.RowCommand>事件，而<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>控制引發<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.ItemCommand>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-111">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.RowCommand> event, whereas the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.ItemCommand> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="575da-112">若要指定要顯示的按鈕類型，請使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase.ButtonType%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-112">To specify the type of button to display, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase.ButtonType%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="575da-113">若要顯示或隱藏的標頭區段<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase>物件、 設定<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase.ShowHeader%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-113">To show or hide the header section of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase> object, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase.ShowHeader%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="575da-114">某些資料繫結控制項 (例如<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>控制項) 即可顯示或隱藏只控制項的整個標頭區段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-114">Some data-bound controls (such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control) can show or hide only the entire header section of the control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="575da-115">不支援這些資料繫結控制項<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase.ShowHeader%2A>個別按鈕欄位的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-115">These data-bound controls do not support the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonFieldBase.ShowHeader%2A> property for an individual button field.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="575da-116">顯示或隱藏的整個標頭區段的資料繫結控制項 （如果有的話），請使用`ShowHeader`控制項的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="575da-116">To show or hide the entire header section of a data-bound control (if available), use the `ShowHeader` property for the control.</span></span>  
  
